name: Darth Vader - Dark Lord of the Sith (Hyperspace)
cleanName: Darth Vader Dark Lord of the Sith Hyperspace
extDescription:
Action [1, T]: If you played a [Villainy] card this phase, deal 1 damage to a unit and 1 damage to a base. Epic Action: If you control 7 or more resources, deploy this leader. (Flip him, ready him, and move him to the ground arena.)

[Deployed Leader Unit]
On Attack: You may deal 2 damage to a unit.

name: Luke Skywalker - Faithful Friend (Hyperspace)
extDescription:
Action [1, T]: Give a Shield token to a [Heroism] unit you played this phase. Epic Action: If you control 6 or more resources, deploy this leader. (Flip him, ready him, and move him to the ground arena.)

[Deployed Leader Unit]
On Attack: You may give another unit a Shield token.
